        <p>Introduction to discrete probability. The first part of the class was a quiz on discrete probability.</p>
<p>Notes originally by <a href="/users/xiamx">@xiamx</a>, with some formatting/language changes by <a href="/users/dellsystem">@dellsystem</a>.</p>
<div class="toc">
<ul>
